description: Alexa will pick a number between 1-100.  It is up to you to guess what the number is.  Don't worry Alexa will let you know if your guess is greater than or less than the number.
name: Guess the Number
shortDescription: Guess the number between 1-100.  Alexa will let you know if your guess is greater than or less than the number. Start by saying, "Alexa, play guess the number!"
